						               													<description>There was a devasted planet called Earth.&amp;#10;Once were habitated by human beings, and not only: then they came.&amp;#10;Pugs. All over it!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Planet of the Pugs is a cooperative game for 2 up to 6 survivors, running time about 20'-30', 8+.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;During their turn, players can play up 2 action (a mandatory one + an optional one) then the Pugs run their cards, to determine Devastation.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Mandatory Action: &amp;#10;- Draw 2 cards&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Optional Actions: &amp;#10;- Play 1 card from the hand&amp;#10;- Block Devastation &amp;ndash; discard 4 copies of the same object to turn down by 1 level the Devastation and take a Special Relic&amp;#10;- Switch Object with other player&amp;#10;&amp;#10;World Action:&amp;#10;- Draw many Devastation cards, looking to the players&amp;rsquo; cards and to reached level.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Devastation bar has 12 levels and 4 steps.&amp;#10;Each step add a difficulty level like not to talk at all or play cards from other player hand.&amp;#10;The more Devastation bar increase the more World Action will increase too.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Three Ending Game Condition&amp;#10;&amp;bull; SURVIVE: the players get up to 5 Special Relics to create the Final Defense!&amp;#10;&amp;bull; DEATH: a player lose 3 life points&amp;#10;&amp;bull; DEVASTATION: the Devastation Counter reach the Max level&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
